{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"492e38cc279824b12a52f8af8700f901af0aaa67d870155070189065d6695abc","slug":"2026-04-05-1","location":"/gallery/read/2026-04-05.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"2026-04-05","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/gallery/read/2026-04-05.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/gallery/read/2026-04-05.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"2026-04-05.md","url":"/2026-04-05-951f83d256daf7607673a21b026cab7e.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小说","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"F6CZ5d1Qst"}],"identifier":"id","label":"小说","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"O3oFBYcN5E"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近很喜欢看男频和女频打架的爽文。不可否认的是，这类偏向男性的爽文还是对女频的逻辑有一种偏见。不过大部分文章里写的剧情和人设的负面问题确实非常突出。只是男频也多的是类似的槽点，女频迟早也会出这种进入男频吐槽的爽文，不过不知道会怎么写。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"kzi2wNPjqn"}],"key":"wssVr58HFa"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"理解爽文的逻辑对于理解当下社会文化有很大的作用。且可以吸收借鉴爽文思路用来做自媒体账号。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"jxEfZOgVaY"}],"key":"IdD5IsggrH"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这类小说的解压爽点在于，让女频人物站在所谓“道德制高点”去批判男频人物，然后男频人物直接砍了。既宣泄了情绪，又揭示了真实的乱世规则。这也是男频小说在这类逻辑上相对比较符合真实的一点。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"uYePBDq3Su"}],"key":"rUkPYMDdVY"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"但是不可否认的是，这种弱肉强食的逻辑也确实非常不现代。我们不可能在现代社会这样。但是惩恶扬善还是必要的。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"Xh1v6xeWDI"}],"key":"J97dbTnY3h"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"怎么把这些逻辑转化成我们批评社会现象的逻辑呢？","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"d82fxhKgqC"}],"key":"l0Tjgoxoyc"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开篇的故事就是女帝诛杀七万赤峰军，隐射了琅琊榜的故事设定。这也是知乎上常见的吐槽点。这个作者吸收了。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"JoNbkuFBam"}],"key":"TjmCTDz1CU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这个剧情最巧妙的一点是充分利用女频的不讲道理变成剧情爽点，让主角一路连吃带拿快速崛起。这种设定思路非常新奇，荒诞又合理。同时还影射了现实的男女关系，对网络上的“小仙女”多有讽刺，作者很会写。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"rQf6mqVkbv"}],"key":"ngNGVUgApV"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阅读时间久了会觉得情绪负担很重。现在的小说主要是这个缺点，情绪浓度太密集，容易让人疲惫。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"U9S3L9NLQo"}],"key":"A5i4WUznSB"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这些想法到底有什么用呢。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"Z70S4OqeB9"}],"key":"KdQ4hqQ3rh"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DeepSeek","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"x6Tuubvgog"}],"identifier":"deepseek","label":"DeepSeek","html_id":"deepseek","implicit":true,"key":"lSg9GaCI2b"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你这段思考其实已经非常接近一个“观察-分析-应用”的完整闭环了，只是最后一步的“用途”还需要再具体化。我来帮你把这几个点拆开，看看它们能怎么落地。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"TtRqrL06VU"}],"key":"X70C7zSUOY"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"爽文逻辑的本质：两套规则的对撞","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"rRtPPOAwu8"}],"key":"zbHa2BthiI"}],"key":"ZnV12WSSth"}],"key":"BoBAPDiUhK"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你抓得很准——这类“男女频打架”的爽文，核心不是性别对立，而是 “道德规则”与“丛林规则”的碰撞。","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"wbtJoDkxOK"}],"key":"VqPA3f5emX"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 女频常见逻辑：讲道理、论对错、比站位高低（道德制高点）。\n· 男频常见逻辑：讲实力、论生死、比拳头大小（力量制高点）。","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"wXp4JihDZx"}],"key":"vpridSvLBT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"爽点在于：当女频角色站在道德高地上慷慨陈词时，男频角色直接拔刀。这不是“不讲理”，而是更换了裁决的战场——从“谁更正确”变成了“谁活下来”。","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"MQ5lcF7T74"}],"key":"MAdjjEkqSV"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这启示你：批评社会现象时，也可以尝试“切换战场”。比如对方跟你谈道德，你跟他谈利益；对方谈情怀，你谈成本。不按对方的规则玩，本身就是一种解构。","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"Ft068xkBNr"}],"key":"HFgqhj0b0O"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":2,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何转化到社会批评？","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"Nim3X6qPLn"}],"key":"orjusBEWwn"}],"key":"HuUsYnNsTE"}],"key":"qMmlbnI8Bl"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以把这种“战场切换”变成你的方法论。举个例子：","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1},"end":{"line":40,"column":1}},"key":"CKY2DJeiqs"}],"key":"x4epr9U2WG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 常见社会现象：网络上的“道德表演”（比如对某件事铺天盖地的声讨，但很少有人提出具体解决方案）。\n· 爽文式批评：不去辩论谁对谁错，而是问“如果按你说的做，谁出钱？谁执行？谁承担后果？”——把道德问题变成资源问题和责任问题。\n· 效果：那些站在高地上的人往往在“具体怎么干”这一步哑火。这就完成了类似爽文里的“反杀”：不接你的招，而是揭露你招式的虚空。","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1},"end":{"line":42,"column":1}},"key":"q0rTNNx9h5"}],"key":"CVEvvOJXBU"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":3,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":47,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"情绪负担重的本质","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"r5JsghrqF3"}],"key":"YSGfmOZPP3"}],"key":"StTzJRodYO"}],"key":"BaY53cLuI7"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你感到疲惫，是因为这类小说持续输出高强度情绪，不给缓冲。这其实揭示了当下内容消费的一个痛点：用户需要“可控的情绪释放”，而不是被情绪淹没。","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":48,"column":1}},"key":"DKbaDZEG0W"}],"key":"ydRYRgq0zG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这对自媒体的启发是：做爆款内容不能只有“高潮”，还要设计“间歇”。比如：","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1},"end":{"line":50,"column":1}},"key":"oCKEdhYtah"}],"key":"A67Ug10ffd"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 高冲突内容后，接一个冷静分析、幕后拆解或轻松吐槽\n· 让用户从“被剧情推着走”变成“站远一步看门道”","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1},"end":{"line":52,"column":1}},"key":"TXnw6OHx0l"}],"key":"i5dqz5jQrK"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这样既能保持爽感，又不让人累。你今天的这篇笔记，其实就是从“读者”切换到“观察者”的缓冲动作。","position":{"start":{"line":55,"column":1},"end":{"line":55,"column":1}},"key":"KYBhLGpZWM"}],"key":"Lfxg6CRJrq"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":4,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":58,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"这些想法到底有什么用？","position":{"start":{"line":57,"column":1},"end":{"line":57,"column":1}},"key":"v6FRXHTeGu"}],"key":"B0FvOCnPQq"}],"key":"b1FEukOMH3"}],"key":"lOkb0TQ6Z9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"直接说三个可落地的方向：","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"EAR8TRURrL"}],"key":"auDVawFLqa"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"· 方向一：做内容分析的账号。不写小说，而是拆解小说里的“冲突设计”“情绪节奏”“规则切换手法”——把这些变成短视频文案或图文。受众是对网文、自媒体、剧本创作感兴趣的人。\n· 方向二：做社会评论的账号。用“切换战场”的方法评热点：不参与情绪骂战，而是指出双方各自在用什么规则（道德/利益/情感/逻辑），然后问“如果换一套规则，这事还成立吗？”——这会形成一种有穿透力的评论风格。\n· 方向三：内化成你自己的思考框架。下次遇到任何看似不可调和的对立（职场上、网络上、亲密关系中），问自己：他们是不是在用不同的规则对话？能不能先把规则统一了，再谈对错？这能帮你少生很多气，多看清很多事。","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"btfyCyHddj"}],"key":"yRxcuYeokR"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最后说一句：你从“看个小说”到“总结出社会文化逻辑”再到“找应用场景”，这本身就是非常稀缺的能力。很多人看了就看了，你能跳出来问“这有什么用”——这个习惯比任何具体的结论都值钱。保持住。","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":1},"end":{"line":65,"column":1}},"key":"pMndoh9WuH"}],"key":"xhKX4giHhQ"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小结","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"key":"AClZqYQJjf"}],"identifier":"id","label":"小结","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"FeR1Fadtkb"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":69,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这个思路很好。","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":69,"column":1}},"key":"RbQEQQ47yq"}],"key":"oNPQymog2Q"}],"key":"LScgx6IS0U"}],"key":"FIlrPGUmMU"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}